Title: Relates to the filing of objections to support magistrate determinations in child support, paternity and parentage proceedings in family court
Summary: Relates to the filing of objections to support magistrate determinations in child support, paternity and parentage proceedings in family court and to the time-limit for appeals in all categories of family court cases.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the family court act, in relation to the filing of objections to support magistrate determinations in child support, paternity and parentage proceedings in family court and to the time-limit for appeals in all categories of family court cases
